data.description:
Welcome to your new home! Nestled in a wonderful neighborhood, this stunning residence has recently undergone a makeover! The interior of the house has been beautifully repainted, the roof is 2020 and HVAC is 2015. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a magnificent kitchen that has been completely renovated. Every detail has been carefully considered, resulting in a modern, functional, space that will inspire your culinary adventures. With brand new appliances, sleep countertops, and ample storage, this kitchen is a true masterpiece. Beyond the kitchen, the rest of the house exudes a sense of warmth and comfort. The open floorpan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating an inviting environment for both, relaxation and entertaining, Natural light floods through the windows, illuminating the elegant finishes and creating a delightful atmosphere throughout. 
The great neighborhoods surrounding this home adds to its allure. 

Schedule your showing today!
